	     <p>安装Ruby</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/documentation/installation/</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get install ruby-full
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>安装jekyll</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>gem install jekyll bundler
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>下载主题并进入主题目录， 安装相关依赖</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>vim Gemfile

<span class="nb">source</span> <span class="s2">"http://gems.ruby-china.com"</span>

bundle update
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>bundle exec jekyll serve</p>

<p>修改文章页面的宽度(代码能放得下)</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>assets/css/screen

.post<span class="o">{</span>
    width: 100%<span class="p">;</span>
    max-width: 810px<span class="p">;</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>图片与文章等宽</p>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.post-content</span> <span class="nt">img</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nl">max-width</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">100%</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>设置摘要分隔符</p>

<p>在配置文件_config.yml文件中配置摘要分割符excerpt_separator，例如:</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="na">excerpt_separator</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">&lt;!--</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">more</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">--&gt;'</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>修改<code class="highlighter-rouge">_includes/loop.html</code>中相关内容:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;p&gt;

修改为:

&lt;p&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>标签管理:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>.post-meta a <span class="o">{</span>
    color: <span class="c">#9EABB3;</span>
    text-decoration: none<span class="p">;</span>
<span class="o">}</span>

.post-meta a <span class="o">{</span>
    color: <span class="c">#9EABB3;</span>
    text-decoration: none<span class="p">;</span>
    margin-right: 3px<span class="p">;</span>
    padding: 2px 7px<span class="p">;</span>
    border-radius: 5px<span class="p">;</span>
    border: <span class="c">#E3E9ED 1px solid;</span>
    font-size: 1.3rem<span class="p">;</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>文章页面管理:</p>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.post-template.post-header</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nl">margin-bottom</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">3.4rem</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>标签管理(loop.html)</p>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">去掉</span><span class="nt">on</span> <span class="err">以及</span><span class="o">,</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

